snippet.title: Madison VR - Official Announcement Trailer | Future Games Show 2023
snippet.description:
Madison VR is a survival horror VR game that utilizes an instant camera in your virtual hands that bridges the gap between our world and the unknown. Snap photos, develop them by yourself to solve puzzles, explore the shadows, and more. Madison VR is launching soon for PlayStation VR2 and SteamVR.

#SummerOfGaming
